Enki - A Content Management System

Project goals

Provide a modern CMS that:
  * Delivers very high-performance pages to end users
  * Enable dynamic experiences for users without comprosing performance 
  * Allow site maintainers to easily add/edit content and layouts

Planned features for site mainters:
  * Easy layout engine 
  * Role based access 
  * Easy to use WYSIWYG content editing

Planned features for developers:
  * Automatic CSS/style optimization
  * Automatic JavaScript optimization
  * Automatic local static or CDN deployment
  * Workflow for pagelets
  * Cache controls
  * Layout ordering
  * Early flush options
  * Dependency resolution

Default Pagelets:
  * Free HTML
  * "Safe" HTML
  * Commenting system
  * Images
